100 void setPoseForDirection(int direction, geometry_msgs::PoseStamped& start_pose,double distance)
101 {
102  geometry_msgs::Quaternion quat;
103  switch(direction)
104  {
106  case ARC_DOWN :
107  quat = tf::createQuaternionMsgFromRollPitchYaw(angles::from_degrees(ROTATION_STEP),angles::from_degrees(0),angles::from_degrees(0)); //Turn down
108  start_pose.header.frame_id=END_EFF_FRAME;
109  start_pose.pose.position.x=0;
110  start_pose.pose.position.y=0.01; // Slightly up
111  start_pose.pose.position.z=-0.01; // Slightly back
112  start_pose.pose.orientation = quat;
113  break;
114  case ARC_UP :
115  quat = tf::createQuaternionMsgFromRollPitchYaw(angles::from_degrees(-ROTATION_STEP),angles::from_degrees(0),angles::from_degrees(0));
116  start_pose.header.frame_id=END_EFF_FRAME;
117  start_pose.pose.position.x=0;
118  start_pose.pose.position.y=-0.01;
119  start_pose.pose.position.z=0.01;
120  start_pose.pose.orientation = quat;
121  break;
122  case TRANSLATE_BACK :
123  quat = tf::createQuaternionMsgFromRollPitchYaw(angles::from_degrees(0),angles::from_degrees(0),angles::from_degrees(0));
124  start_pose.header.frame_id=END_EFF_FRAME;
125  start_pose.pose.position.x=0;
126  start_pose.pose.position.y=0;
127  start_pose.pose.position.z=-distance;
128  start_pose.pose.orientation = quat;
129  break;
130  case TRANSLATE_FRONT :
131  quat = tf::createQuaternionMsgFromRollPitchYaw(angles::from_degrees(0),angles::from_degrees(0),angles::from_degrees(0));
132  start_pose.header.frame_id=END_EFF_FRAME;
133  start_pose.pose.position.x=0;
134  start_pose.pose.position.y=0;
135  start_pose.pose.position.z=distance;
136  start_pose.pose.orientation = quat;
137  break;
138  case TRANSLATE_RIGHT :
139  quat = tf::createQuaternionMsgFromRollPitchYaw(angles::from_degrees(0),angles::from_degrees(0),angles::from_degrees(0));
140  start_pose.header.frame_id=END_EFF_FRAME;
141  start_pose.pose.position.x=-distance;
142  start_pose.pose.position.y=0;
143  start_pose.pose.position.z=0;
144  start_pose.pose.orientation = quat;
145  break;
146  case TRANSLATE_LEFT :
147  quat = tf::createQuaternionMsgFromRollPitchYaw(angles::from_degrees(0),angles::from_degrees(0),angles::from_degrees(0));
148  start_pose.header.frame_id=END_EFF_FRAME;

150  start_pose.pose.position.y=0;

159 geometry_msgs::TwistStamped getTwistForDirection(int direction)
160 {
161  geometry_msgs::TwistStamped twist;
162  twist.header.stamp=ros::Time::now();
163  twist.header.frame_id="j2s7s300_link_7";
164  twist.header.seq=seq++;
165  switch(direction)
166  {
167  case ARC_DOWN:
168  ROS_INFO("Arc down");
169  twist.twist.linear.z=VEL_LIN_MAX;
170  twist.twist.angular.x=VEL_ANG_MAX;
171  break;
172 
173  case ARC_UP:
174  ROS_INFO("Arc up");
175  twist.twist.linear.z=-VEL_LIN_MAX;
176  twist.twist.angular.x=-VEL_ANG_MAX;
177  break;
178 
179  case TRANSLATE_LEFT:
180  // ROS_INFO("Translate left");
181  twist.twist.linear.x=VEL_LIN_MAX;
182  break;
183 
184  case TRANSLATE_RIGHT:
185 // ROS_INFO("Translate right");
186  twist.twist.linear.x=-VEL_LIN_MAX;
187  break;
188 
189  case ROTATE_DOWN:
190  ROS_INFO("Rotate down");
191  twist.twist.angular.x=VEL_ANG_MAX;
192  break;
193 
194  case TRANSLATE_UP:
195  // ROS_INFO("Translate up");
196  twist.twist.linear.z=VEL_LIN_MAX;
197  break;
198 
199  case TRANSLATE_DOWN:
200 // ROS_INFO("Translate down");
201  twist.twist.linear.z=-VEL_LIN_MAX;
202  break;
203 
204  case ROTATE_LEFT:
205  ROS_INFO("Rotate left");
206  twist.twist.angular.z=-VEL_ANG_MAX;
207  break;
208 
209  case ROTATE_RIGHT:
210  ROS_INFO("Rotate right");
211  twist.twist.angular.z=VEL_ANG_MAX;
212  break;
213 
214  case ARC_LEFT: // Translate up, translate right, rotate left
215  ROS_INFO("Arc left: Feed water");
216  twist.twist.linear.z=VEL_LIN_MAX;
217  // twist.twist.linear.x=-VEL_LIN_MAX;
218  twist.twist.angular.z=-VEL_ANG_MAX;
219  break;
220 
221  case ARC_RIGHT: // Translate down, translate left, rotate right
222  ROS_INFO("Arc right: Retreat");
223  twist.twist.linear.z=-VEL_LIN_MAX;
224  // twist.twist.linear.x=VEL_LIN_MAX;
225  twist.twist.angular.z=VEL_ANG_MAX;
226  break;
227 
228  }
229  return twist;
230 }

232 bool isForceSafe()
233 {
234  double local_force_f,local_force_b;
235  lock_force.lock();
236  local_force_f=force_f;
237  local_force_b=force_b;
238  lock_force.unlock();
239 
240  if (local_force_f >= FORCE_F_PAIN_THRESH || local_force_b >= FORCE_F_PAIN_THRESH)
241  return false;
242  else
243  return true;
244 }

246 void publishTwistForDuration(geometry_msgs::TwistStamped twist_msg, double duration)
247 {
248  ros::Time time_start = ros::Time::now();
249  while (ros::Time::now() - time_start < ros::Duration(duration))
250  {
251  ros::spinOnce();
252  if(isForceSafe())
253  {
254  cmd_vel.publish(twist_msg);
255  }
256  else
257  {
258  ROS_WARN("PAIN THRESHOLD BREACHED, ABORTING SEQUENCE!!!");
259  break;
260  }
261  }

264 void positionControlDriveForDirection(int direction, double distance)
265 {
266  geometry_msgs::PoseStamped start_pose, pose_in_base;
267  tf::TransformListener tf_listener;
268  //Wait for TF buffer to fill up
269  ros::Duration(0.25).sleep();
270  ros::Rate loop_rate(10);
271 
272  while(ros::ok())
273  {
274  try
275  {
276 
277  lock_pose.lock();
278  start_pose = current_pose;
279  lock_pose.unlock();
280 
281 
282  setPoseForDirection(direction, start_pose, distance);
283 
284  tf_listener.transformPose(BASE_FRAME,start_pose,pose_in_base);
285  break;
286 
287  }
288  catch (tf::ExtrapolationException e)
289  {
290 // ROS_INFO_STREAM("Waiting for transform "
291 // << e.what()
292 // );
293  }
294  ros::spinOnce();
295  loop_rate.sleep();
296  }
297 
298  cmd_pos.publish(pose_in_base);
299 }

301 void moveCup(int direction, double duration=VEL_CMD_DURATION, double distance=0.1)
302 {
303  //ROS_INFO_STREAM("Calling moveCup. Direction : " << direction << " Duration : " << duration << " Distance: " << distance);
304  if (direction==TRANSLATE_BACK

306  //|| direction==TRANSLATE_LEFT

309  {
310  positionControlDriveForDirection(direction, distance);
311  return;
312  }
313  else

315  geometry_msgs::TwistStamped twist_msg = getTwistForDirection(direction);

370 bool checkUpperAngleThreshold()
371 {
372  geometry_msgs::PoseStamped temp_pose;
373 
374  lock_pose.lock();
375  temp_pose=current_pose;
376  lock_pose.unlock();
377 
378  double temp_roll, temp_pitch, temp_yaw;
379  getRPYFromQuaternionMSG(temp_pose.pose.orientation,temp_roll, temp_pitch, temp_yaw);
380 
381  if ( angles::to_degrees(temp_pitch) > UPPER_FEED_ANGLE_THRESH )
382  {
383  ROS_WARN_STREAM("MAX UPPER FEED ANGLE REACHED");
384  return false;
385  }
386  else
387  {
388  return true;
389  }
390 }
391 
392 bool checkLowerAngleThreshold()
393 {
394  geometry_msgs::PoseStamped temp_pose;
395 
396  lock_pose.lock();
397  temp_pose=current_pose;
398  lock_pose.unlock();
399 
400  double temp_roll, temp_pitch, temp_yaw;
401  getRPYFromQuaternionMSG(temp_pose.pose.orientation,temp_roll, temp_pitch, temp_yaw);
402 
403  if (angles::to_degrees(temp_pitch) < LOWER_FEED_ANGLE_THRESH )
404  {
405  ROS_WARN_STREAM("MAX LOWER FEED ANGLE REACHED");
406  return false;
407  }
408  else
409  {
410  return true;

414 int main(int argc, char **argv)
415 {
416  ros::init(argc, argv, "feeder_sideways");
417  ros::NodeHandle nh;
418 
419  tf::TransformListener tf_listener;
420 
421  ros::Subscriber sub = nh.subscribe("/force_values", 1000, forceGrabber);
422  cmd_vel = nh.advertise<geometry_msgs::TwistStamped>("/RobotControl/VelocityControl", 1000);
423  cmd_pos = nh.advertise<geometry_msgs::PoseStamped>("/RobotControl/PoseControl", 1000);
424  ros::Subscriber tool_pose = nh.subscribe("/j2s7s300_driver/out/tool_pose",1000, poseGrabber );

426 
427  ros::Rate loop_rate(9);
428 
429  waitForPoseDataAvailable();
430 
431  double local_force_f,local_force_b;
432  bool print_once_only=true;
433 
434  lock_pose.lock();
435  initial_pose=current_pose;
436  lock_pose.unlock();
437 
439 // moveCup(TRANSLATE_UP, VEL_CMD_DURATION*0.5);
440  moveCup(TRANSLATE_RIGHT, VEL_CMD_DURATION*0.2);
441  moveCup(ARC_LEFT, VEL_CMD_DURATION);
442 
443 
444 
445  while(ros::ok())
446  {
447  ros::spinOnce();
448 
449  lock_force.lock();

451  local_force_b=force_b;
452  lock_force.unlock();
453 
455  if (local_force_f >= FORCE_F_TRIGGER_THRESH && local_force_b <FORCE_B_TRIGGER_THRESH && checkUpperAngleThreshold())
456  {
457  moveCup(TRANSLATE_UP, VEL_CMD_DURATION*0.2);
458  moveCup(TRANSLATE_RIGHT, VEL_CMD_DURATION*0.1);
459  moveCup(ARC_LEFT, VEL_CMD_DURATION);
460  print_once_only=true;
461  }
462  else if (local_force_f <FORCE_F_TRIGGER_THRESH && local_force_b>=FORCE_B_TRIGGER_THRESH && checkLowerAngleThreshold())
463  {
464  moveCup(TRANSLATE_DOWN, VEL_CMD_DURATION*0.2);
465  moveCup(TRANSLATE_LEFT, VEL_CMD_DURATION*0.1);
466  moveCup(ARC_RIGHT, VEL_CMD_DURATION);
467  print_once_only=true;
468  }
469  // else if (local_force_f >= FORCE_F_TRIGGER_THRESH && local_force_b >=FORCE_B_TRIGGER_THRESH)
470  else if (local_force_f >= FORCE_BOTH_FALLBACK && local_force_b >=FORCE_BOTH_FALLBACK)
471  {
472  ROS_WARN("FALLBACK INITIATED, CLOSING NODE");
473  fallBack(initial_pose);
474  break;
475  }
476  else if (print_once_only)
477  {
478  ROS_INFO_STREAM("Do nothing.");
479  print_once_only=false;
480  }
481 
482  loop_rate.sleep();
483  }
484 
485 
486 
487  ros::spinOnce();
488 
489  return 0;
490 }
